OL,3,CThreatened with decapitation - the
OL,4,Cshocking abuse faced by Welsh
OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FThe majority of Welsh politicians have
OL,8,Ffelt unsafe because of their public
OL,9,Frole - with some considering leaving
OL,10,Ftheir roles due to threats and abuse.
OL,12,FITV Cymru Wales' programme asked all
OL,13,FSenedd Members and Wales constituency
OL,14,FMPs how safe they felt due to their
OL,15,Fjob and if they'd ever considered
OL,16,Fquitting as a result.
OL,18,FThree quarters (75%) of those who
OL,19,Fresponded admitted that there were
OL,20,Foccasions when they felt unsafe
OL,21,Fbecause of their role.
