OL,5,Cpoliticians
OL,7,FBut in the last eight years, two MPs `
OL,8,FJo Cox and Sir David Amess ` were
OL,9,Fmurdered as they met their
OL,10,Fconstituents.
OL,12,FPeople in public life feel at risk of
OL,13,Fabuse and intimidation, with one Welsh
OL,14,FMP's office, Jo Stevens, being
OL,15,Ftargeted just last year.
OL,17,F"All this sounds familiar," former
OL,18,Fhome secretary Jacqui Smith, who
OL,19,Fchairs the Jo Cox Foundation, said.
OL,20,F"And the evidence suggests that it's
OL,21,Fgetting worse.
