OL,7,F"It affects everyone but it has a
OL,8,Fdisproportionate effect on women,
OL,9,Fpeople of colour, people from the
OL,10,FLGBT+ community and people with
OL,11,Fdisabilities, the very people we need
OL,12,Fto see more of in politics.
OL,14,F"It doesn't just affect the politician
OL,15,Fthemselves, but their friends and
OL,16,Ffamilies too. It's absolutely
OL,17,Funreasonable for people to have to put
OL,18,Fup with that."
